quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  16,1,"Itegeko ry’Imana rizoshika, rero ntimuyihimirize kuko niyo yisukuye n’ivyoba bigabanutse vyose hamwe nukuyininahaza kwose nukubayi gereranya Imana n’ibindi bintu vyabo bahakanyi b’Imana y’ukuri"
  16,2,"Ibamanurira Abamarayika hamwe n’ubutumwa kw’itegeko ryayo kubo yishakiye mubashumvyi biwe yuko batuza abantu, atawundi akwiye gusengwa atari jewe jenyene gusa, rero nimuntinye"
  16,3,"Niwe yaremye Amajuru n’Isi bimwe vy’ukuri, ari n’iteka ntangere ry’ukuta gereranya Imana n’ibindi bintu vyabo bahakanyi b’Imana"
  16,4,"Niyo yaremye ikiremwa muntu kw’Ima ry’intanga, mukanya ng’uyo wa muntu yabaye umuntu w’amananiza aboneka neza k’umugaragaro"
  16,5,"Niyo yaremye ibikoko, murivyo muharonkeramwo ubushuhe n’ubundi bumaro n’ibindi navyo mukavyikenurako"
  16,6,Mukanezerwa mugihe muzicuye k’umugoroba nomugihe mubiturukije kuja kurisha mugitondo
  16,7,"Nugutwara amatu yanyu iyajana mubisagara mudashobora kuyashikana atari kumakenga n’igorane zihanitse, mu vy’ukuri Umuremyi wanyu n’intore cane kandi niyo nyene imigisha ihagije"
  16,8,"N’ibitwazi vyanyu arizo farasi hamwe n’ibimeze nk’ifarasi hamwe n’indogobwe kugira ngo muvyurireko bisharije, none mwebwe muzorema ivyo mutazi"
  16,9,"Ni hejuru y’Imana kwerekana inzira y’ukuri, kuko hariho izindi nzira zitameze neza, rero iyo Imana ibishaka ntankeka yari kubarongora mwese uko mungana"